[I] KDE Frameworks library that wraps Client and Server Wayland libraries

[T] KWayland is a Qt-style API to interact with the wayland-client API. The API
[T] is Qt-styled removing the needs to interact with a for a Qt developer
[T] uncomfortable low-level C-API.

[U] https://invent.kde.org/plasma/kwayland

[A] The KDE-Team
